  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Poverty mapping of the four municipalities on the basis of following outcomes of UEIP project: Digital Base Map; Cadastral Information System and Superposition of cadastral map to digital base map; geographical Information System incorporating demography, environment, socio-economy etc;\r\n    Gender assessment and need identification on water, sanitation services through focus group discussion, site observation and interaction with targeted population;\r\n    Capacity building of municipalities on pro poor urban governance by orientation to the municipal personnel, workshops at local, regional and national level and training to municipal staff."
    },
